      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SO HE THINKS (3) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a one length third (34.72) behind Mepunga Phantom at this track. Makes plenty of appeal. TIGER ROCKS (1) pinged the lids and led for most of the way to hold a minor placing when second and beaten 1.3 lengths (34.90) at this track in a Grade 5 over 595m. Hard to beat again. VERA JAKIT (7) turned in a better effort at Traralgon last start, finishing third behind Miss Jeckell (33.18) in a Rank Limit - Grade 5. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to be in the finish again. HEY PRESTO (2) can feature with the right run.",
